com.facebook.buck.java

Interface HasJavaSrcs

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidLibraryRule, DefaultJavaLibraryRule, FakeDefaultJavaLibraryRule, JavaTestRule, RobolectricTestRule

    public interface HasJavaSrcs
    A build rule should implement this interface if it has a 'srcs' attribute that lists Java source files.
